# {{PROBLEM}} Method Design Recipe

## 1. Describe the Problem

- User wants to verify that given text starts with a capital letter 
- And ends with a grammatically correct sentence-ending punctuation mark.

## 2. Design the Method Signature

method name and parameter: sentence_checker(text)
return value true or false 

## 3. Create Examples as Tests

sentence_checker("Ruby is awesome!") => true


## 4. Implement the Behaviour

_After each test you write, follow the test-driving process of red, green, refactor to implement the behaviour._
